Pokemon_Platinum_Game Object has all the subclasses
Pokemon_Platinum_Runner runs the game

Supporting classes:
	1. Pokedex: Stores a basic version of all pokemon to reference
	2. Movelist: Stores all the pokemon battles moves
	3. Map_Storage: Stores all the Pokemon_Maps
	4. Trainer_Map_Storage: Stores all the Pokemon_Trainers
	5. Pokemon_Battle_Runner: Creates a pop-up window for a pokemon battles
	6. Pokemon_Battle_Turn: Creates one turn of combat within a pokemon battle
	7. Audio: Plays the corresponding background music for the situation

Notable objects:
	1. Pokemon: used for the pokemon battles
	2. Pokemon_Trainer: battle against them
	3. Player: Extends Pokemon_Trainer with a movement system